      "body" : "@anarcat Luke isn't talking about Bitcoin clients, but about JSON-RPC clients. The JSON-RPC interface is intended to be used by applications, and bitcoind itself just implements a very simple CLI JSON-RPC client (in addition to being a full-blown Bitcoin client). Earlier discussions have suggested writing a more user-friendly python JSON-RPC CLI client, instead of pushing more features into bitcoind,",
