      "body" : "Yes, I understand all that. I read some of the code for bitrpc and the other Python clients out there.\r\n\r\nMy point is that none of those implementations are mature enough. The bitcoind client *is* a JSONRPC client right now and it does a lot of things! It seems to me that making the `bitcoind walletpassphrase` command prompt for a password is a minor improvement that should be implemented, don't you think?",
